{"tid":2116294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法院今明兩天只處理緊急案件指示混亂 職員：休兩日休嚟有乜意思","createTime":"2020-07-20T05:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T05:40:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bffa768ea5ae352d89a5379a1cc31e558588637","tid":2116294,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200720/KIQMDZNQ7GSWBIW5OVHWLLEU2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200720%2FKIQMDZNQ7GSWBIW5OVHWLLEU2Y%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=f10ca2ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200720%2FKIQMDZNQ7GSWBIW5OVHWLLEU2Y%2F&h=33b30426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200720/KIQMDZNQ7GSWBIW5OVHWLLEU2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎確診個案單日破百，政府昨日終宣佈，除了提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，其他公務員在家工作。司法機構則宣佈今明兩天進行的所有聆訊將會延期，除非屬申請保釋或還柙候訊等特殊情況。有「摸門釘」市民理解法庭暫停聆訊的做法，「始終都係人群聚集，都明嘅」；但有職員卻指安排混亂，「休兩日，星期三又正常，休嚟有乜意思，亂到七彩」；亦有市民到庭後獲保安告知聆訊取消，但向法庭登記處查詢後發現聆訊如常。"},{"pid":"0dcf807f9efc694419a9cf9a81c87d114e8eea32","tid":2116294,"uid":202425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"根本個政府落指令做嘢就唔會諗前線人員<br />\n高層落order唔會理下面跟唔跟到"},{"pid":"2d1c89f32b0fea618010fa10730179f0f9b7598b","tid":2116294,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dcf807f9efc694419a9cf9a81c87d114e8eea32","tid":2116294,"uid":202425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"根本個政府落指令做嘢就唔會諗前線人員<br />\n高層落order唔會理下面跟唔跟到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16be9367bd41287d6658cca57da977f8ac213c8c","tid":2116294,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0dcf807f9efc694419a9cf9a81c87d114e8eea32","tid":2116294,"uid":202425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"根本個政府落指令做嘢就唔會諗前線人員<br />\n高層落order唔會理下面跟唔跟到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"&quot;有職員則謂是日安排混亂，「懲教話收唔到指示，唔帶犯，要下午先到」。他又解釋：「舊案唔做，舊案8日bail review（擔保覆核）做，新案on bail唔做，冇bail就做，判刑冇bail都做。我都驚我自己講錯。」&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e132cb499863ab456f98733dd5df62b4786a2d87","tid":2116294,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16be9367bd41287d6658cca57da977f8ac213c8c","tid":2116294,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0dcf807f9efc694419a9cf9a81c87d114e8eea32","tid":2116294,"uid":202425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"根本個政府落指令做嘢就唔會諗前線人員<br />\n高層落order唔會理下面跟唔跟到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"&quot;有職員則謂是日安排混亂，「懲教話收唔到指示，唔帶犯，要下午先到」。他又解釋：「舊案唔做，舊案8日bail review（擔保覆核）做，新案on bail唔做，冇bail就做，判刑冇bail都做。我都驚我自己講錯。」&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}